# PLAYER::INT_TO_PLAYERINDEX

## Summary
Converts an int to a player index

## Parameters
* **INT** arg

## Returns
* **PLAYER_INDEX**

## Notes
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
Simply returns whatever is passed to it (Regardless of whether the handle is valid or not).
